---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 358
  - Title: The Cloud of Unknowing
    Chapter: XLII
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=Act and Essence
  - 641
---
Do this work (of contemplation) evermore without ceasing and without
discretion, and thou shalt know well how to begin and cease in all
other works with a great discretion.
